* * Binds component instance methods. * * Requires the component instance to be passed as first argument. Any additional arguments are optional and specify "matchers" for method/function names.
* * - Any function on the instance with has a name that matches one of the arguments will be bound to the instance. * - The arguments may be either strings or regular expressions. * - The arguments will be flattened, so you can either pass them individually, or as one or more arrays. * - When called with just the instance as a single argument, the default matcher `/^handle/` will be used. * * @param {Object} component - the component instance * @param {...String|...RegExp} [matchKeys = [/^handle/]] - strings or regular expressions matching method names to bind
